quran[10{c,v,t}:
27,89,jo shakhs bhalai le kar aayega usay uss se ziyada behtar sila miley ga aur aisay log uss din ke houlle se mehfooz hon ge
27,90,"aur jo buraii liye hue aeye ga, aisay sab log avndhe mun aag mein phainky jayen ge kya tum log is ke siwa koi aur jaza pa satke ho ke jaissa karo waisa bharo ?"
27,91,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho )"" mujhe to yahi hukum diya gaya hai ke iss shehar ke rab ki bandagi karoon jis ne isay haram banaya hai aur jo har cheez ka maalik hai mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke mein muslim ban kar rahon"
27,92,"aur yeh quran parh kar sunaoon"" ab jo hadaayat ikhtiyar kere ga woh apne hi bhallay ke liye hadaayat ikhtiyar kere ga aur jo gumraah ho uss se keh do ke mein to bas khabardaar kar dainay wala hon"
27,93,"inn se kaho, tareef Allah hi ke liye hai, anqareeb woh tumhe apni nishanain dikha day ga aur tum inhen pehchan lau ge, aur tera rab be khabar nahi hai unn aamaal se jo tum log karte ho"
28,1,toy seen meem
28,2,yeh kitaab Mubin ki ayaat hain
28,3,hum moose aur firaon ka kuch haal theek theek tumhe sanatay hain aisay logon ke faiday ke liye jo imaan layein
28,4,"waqea yeh hai ke firaon ne zameen mein sar kashi ki aur is ke bashindon ko garohoon mein taqseem kar diya un mein se aik giroh ko woh zaleel karta tha, is ke larkoon ko qatal karta aur is ki larkiyon ko jeeta rehne deta tha fi al waqea woh mufsid logon mein se tha"
28,5,aur hum yeh iradah rakhtay thay ke meharbani karen un logon par jo zameen mein zaleel kar ke rakhay gay thay aur inhen peshwa bana den aur unhi ko waris banayen
